  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 60,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Aaronam dſimune\nRadabs un Abijus/ Eeleazars un\nIhtamars.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 61,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Nadabs un Abijus\nbija nomirrufchi/ kad tee ſweſchu\nUgguni preeſch to KUNGU\npeeneffe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 62,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un winno ſkaititi bija di-\nwidesmits trihs tuhſtoschi/ wiſſi\nWihriski/weenu Mehnefi un pah-\nri wezzi / jo tee ne tappe ſkaititi\npee teem Israëta Behrneem / ta-\npehz / ka teem ne kahda Dalliba\nſtarp teem Israëta Behrneem\ntappe dohta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 63,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schee irr tee ſkaititti no\nMohsus un Eeleazara ta Preeste-\nra / kas tohs Israëta Behrnus\neekſch Monba Klajumeem ſkaitti-\nja / pee tahs Jardanas prett Je-\nritu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 64,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ſtarp teem ne bija ne\nweenß/no teem no Mohsus un A-\narona taPreestera ſkaititeemi/kad\ntee tohs Israëta Behrnus eekſch\ntahs Tuḱnefes Sinai ſkaitijufschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 65,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tas KUNGSS bija us\nteem fazzijis : Tee mirtin mirs\nTukfneti / un no teem ne bija ne\nweenß atlizzis / kä Kahlebs / Je-\nwuna Dehls/ un Josuüs Nunna\nDehls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ad peegahje tahs Mei-\ntas Zelaweada/ Eewer-\nDehta/Gileada Dehta,\nta Makira Dehta / ta Dehta Ma-\nnaffus ſtarp Manaffus Rad-\ndeem / Jahsepa Dehta / un ſche-\nirr winna Meitu Wahrdi / Ma-\nëla/ un Noa / un Agla/ un Mi-\nka/ un Tirza.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tahs ſtahweja preeſch-\nMohsus / un preeſch Eeleasara\nta Preestera / un preeſch teen\nWirfneekeim un wiffas Drau-\ndses/ preeſch tahs Sa-eeschana\nTelts Durwin/ un fazzija :\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Muhfu Tehws irr Tukfne-\nfi nomirris / un tahs ne irr biji-\nſtarpan tahs Draudses/ kas pret-\nto KUNGU irr ſapulzejusees/ſtar-\ntahs Korus Draudses/ bet winſc-\nirr ſawã paſchã Noseedsiba na-\nmirris/un winnam ne bija Deht-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kapelz tad muhſu Tehw-\nWahrds ſtarp farveein Raddee-\ntaptu iſdeldehts/ tadeht/ ka tan-\nne bija ne kahds Dehls / dohdee-\nmuns weenu Ihpaſchnmu star-\nimuhſu Tehwa Brahteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Mohsus nefte winu-\nTeefas Mekleschanu tam KUN-\nGAM preeſcha.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad runnaja tas KUNG-\nus Mohsu/ un fazzija :\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tahs Zelaweada Meita-\nruña pareifi/ dohd winnahm we-\nnu Ihpaſchumu ſtarp winnu Teh-\nwa Brahteem/ un preeſch irr wi-\nnahn ſawa Tehwa Ihpaſchumu-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un us teem Israëta Beh-\nneem buhs tewrunnaht / un fa-\nzif-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
